NOTE TO MAINTAINERS — do not publish the repository until this is resolved.

AGPL-3.0 is the *recommended* license for a federated, open social platform: it
keeps the product and any hosted/modified derivatives open, which fits Tacet's
"open before closed" stance. The final choice is a founder decision and may change
before public release.

Before the repository is made public, replace THIS FILE with the full, verbatim
GNU AGPL-3.0 license text, which could not be fetched in the build environment:

    https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt

  e.g.  curl -fsSL https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt -o LICENSE

If a different license is chosen, replace this file accordingly and update any
SPDX identifiers and the README license section.
